Concept	                            Key Info
@interface	                        Used to define a custom annotation
@Retention(RUNTIME)	                Required to access annotations via reflection
@Target({ElementType.METHOD})	    Limits where the annotation can be applied
@Repeatable	                        Allows multiple instances of the same annotation on one element
@Inherited	                        Applies to classes only, propagates to subclasses
Reflection	                        Used to access annotation metadata at runtime